#: ../../odop.rst:6
msgid ""
"To allow modularized code, Taichi borrow some concepts from object-"
"oriented programming (OOP)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../odop.rst:8
msgid ""
"For convenience, let's call the hybrid scheme **objective data-oriented "
"programming** (ODOP)."
